            "icon": "none",
            "icon_width": 20,
            "title": "What‘s in the box?",
            "content": "<p>-Yozma E-bike*1<br/>-48V 23.4Ah Lithium-Ion*1<br/>-Battery Charger*1<br/>-Assembly Tools*1<br/>-Pedals*2<br/>-Handle Bars Shipped Installed On Bike*1<br/>-User Manual*1<br/>-Number plate decals*1<br/>Note: Please keep this box for at least 30 days in case of return or after-sales service.</p>",
