          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Important Notice:<br/></strong><br/>Thank you so much for your amazing support! We truly appreciate your enthusiasm for Yozma. Due to overwhelming demand, our stock has sold out, and we have now opened pre-sale. Orders placed now are expected to ship in 15 business days after your order is placed.</p><p>Once the products arrive at the warehouse, we will ship them in the order they were placed. We really appreciate your patience and understanding, and we are doing everything we can to fulfill your order as quickly as possible.😊</p><p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to us at support@yozmasport.com.</p>"
