    "multi_column_Lf4Qra": {
      "type": "multi-column-slide",
      "blocks": {
        "item_79AXFi": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/e28a42c4475362c949415a1c17dcc923_b767df6b-6d63-4ad3-ae27-f3362ef528ba.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "2600W Mid-drive Motor",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>Our electric motorcycles are equipped with high-performance motors(mid-drive motor)that deliver more powerful performance than similar products on the market.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_rB33db": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7ecc40279fd871bac0e0d11e210a632b_a6f1aa97-52ca-4421-835f-1d1e24b98a11.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Automotive Grade Chip Battery",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>The battery module can only be disassembled using a dedicated key, which eliminates the risk of unauthorized disassembly.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_DiYNPz": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/af44032b90374e0b22a4e0995a8872ff_3ddc8a3d-6bc3-420e-a0ff-c855471c54b7.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Nitrogen Air Shock Absorber",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>Featuring an independent suspension paired with a high-stiffness air spring shock absorber, it effortlessly absorbs shocks and elevates your riding comfort to a whole new level.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_EDFb9C": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/e995b0ca9bf3913beacb2fdc5ded1b00_a621764c-8424-4090-bfd9-121a421a98f2.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Heavy-duty Hydraulic Brakes",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>Hydraulic brakes for confident control. Advanced suspension with oil-hydraulic nitrogen shocks keeps your ride smooth—even when the road gets wild.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_brXime": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/810a8a9d308e487c64e8273045771c01_4e122d8e-af78-4924-9bd3-e31d3006d872.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Front Hydraulic Suspension",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>The front hydraulic suspension fork smooths out bumps and rough trails, keeping your ride steady and comfortable wherever you go.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_xWQbjA": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/01015e06a73ed3af9db636c83b4596cf_a745052b-6560-46c2-a641-c2f3b8781346.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Dual-size Puncture Resistant Fat Tires",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>The tires are made with a highly wear-resistant formula that offers an additional 2,000 kilometers of mileage compared to similar models.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_gmtxrx": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/0cdc11940874c6e4edb16b027f443614_e34048f3-f18f-45b0-8663-45776a887627.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "More readable Smart Display",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>It has an innovative split design with an independent handlebar and instrument layout.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_QCEbzc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5e1cfa007d9edd0c511e754398cedb5a_eb706811-9a4b-4d03-bfb3-3f40b299ff64.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Motor Style Seat with Quick Release",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>The IN10’s 72 cm seat height suits riders from 120 to 175 cm. Combined with a lightweight body and superior load capacity, it delivers standout performance in its class.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        },
        "item_Cij7n6": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/fb5503765821ab69c2789f65123a00a2_5e698fb5-25c2-47ef-b544-d7d9c5c40ab6.jpg",
            "show_controls": false,
            "column_size": "3",
            "title": "Stable Kickstand",
            "heading_tag": "h5",
            "content": "<p>The sturdy, cast-steel foot pedals provide stability and peace of mind on every trip.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": "",
            "link_style": "link"
          }
        }
      },
